  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i><strong>Little Chef: Cozy Cooking</strong></i>, each level is a cozy puzzle sandbox set in its own unique kitchen. You’ll unlock recipes by experimenting with ingredients, mastering hands-on cooking mechanics, and solving environment-based puzzles designed around the space itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/fa5b78fd19a7d7d92f7cb0f7ca909037.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of a sweet croissant being made by tossing a croissant and nutella into the oven.\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/fa5b78fd19a7d7d92f7cb0f7ca909037.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook everything from comfort foods and gourmet dishes to strange, surprising experiments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with satisfying physics as every ingredient and object reacts in fun, surprising ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve playful kitchen puzzles to uncover hidden ingredients, secrets, and new ways to cook.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect fun achievements that reward curiosity, chaos, and breaking the rules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow a heartfelt story by unlocking each recipe, from childhood favourites to brand-new creations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIX & MATCH INGREDIENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag, drop, toss, or gently place ingredients into pots, ovens, and pans. Combining the right ones unlocks new recipes, good and bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/d58c1ede755d8971e736d28ebeff6e8a.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of banana pancakes being made by tossing milk, banana and eggs into the pot.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/d58c1ede755d8971e736d28ebeff6e8a.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY WITH PHYSICS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything has weight, motion and personality. Drag and drop items, or throw them around. Explore, experiment, and see what secrets you can uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/3b85ca22a81af1858be3e2f48a529443.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of books being picked up out of the book shelf and dropped.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/3b85ca22a81af1858be3e2f48a529443.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE COZY PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not all ingredients are easy to find. Some are hidden, others are locked away, and solving these puzzles might mean thinking creatively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/7d6f795a04d78afebd5c5bbb69f96356.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of a coffee can being dragged left and right, pouring out a lot of coffee\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/7d6f795a04d78afebd5c5bbb69f96356.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i><strong>Little Chef: Cozy Cooking</strong></i>, each level is a cozy puzzle sandbox set in its own unique kitchen. You’ll unlock recipes by experimenting with ingredients, mastering hands-on cooking mechanics, and solving environment-based puzzles designed around the space itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/fa5b78fd19a7d7d92f7cb0f7ca909037.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of a sweet croissant being made by tossing a croissant and nutella into the oven.\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/fa5b78fd19a7d7d92f7cb0f7ca909037.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook everything from comfort foods and gourmet dishes to strange, surprising experiments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with satisfying physics as every ingredient and object reacts in fun, surprising ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve playful kitchen puzzles to uncover hidden ingredients, secrets, and new ways to cook.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect fun achievements that reward curiosity, chaos, and breaking the rules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow a heartfelt story by unlocking each recipe, from childhood favourites to brand-new creations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIX & MATCH INGREDIENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag, drop, toss, or gently place ingredients into pots, ovens, and pans. Combining the right ones unlocks new recipes, good and bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/d58c1ede755d8971e736d28ebeff6e8a.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of banana pancakes being made by tossing milk, banana and eggs into the pot.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/d58c1ede755d8971e736d28ebeff6e8a.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY WITH PHYSICS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything has weight, motion and personality. Drag and drop items, or throw them around. Explore, experiment, and see what secrets you can uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/3b85ca22a81af1858be3e2f48a529443.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of books being picked up out of the book shelf and dropped.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/3b85ca22a81af1858be3e2f48a529443.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE COZY PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not all ingredients are easy to find. Some are hidden, others are locked away, and solving these puzzles might mean thinking creatively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/7d6f795a04d78afebd5c5bbb69f96356.poster.avif?t=1774095188\" aria-label=\"A gif of a coffee can being dragged left and right, pouring out a lot of coffee\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/7d6f795a04d78afebd5c5bbb69f96356.webm?t=1774095188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
