      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 157,
      "review_text": "This game is super cute! The visuals are very nice, the recipies are creative and hillarious at times. I had fun figuring them out and solving the puzzles for new ingridients. The story is also charming and can be relaitable for many people. I love the fact that the story is conveyed to us through the recipes we make and as we progress, we get to know the main character, her aspirations, thoughts and what she's going through with people around her. Overall very cozy indeed and nicely done. :)",
      "timestamp_created": 1774098109
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221293676",
      "author_steamid": "76561198084872742",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 145,
      "review_text": "Fun little cozy game to play when you're bored. Definitely still needs the extra content, but you can see the intention for it is there already.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774113224
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221321167",
      "author_steamid": "76561198271884850",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 215,
      "review_text": "A really sweet game. There is a lot of attention spent on small details. You know it's good when it can be a delight just to mess around and swing around ingredients, utensils and other kitches supplies. Loved the puzzle elements in each level and all the wacky recipes. Although I did get stuck on a few tricky recipes, the current balance seems to be okay. Looking forward on new levels, new recipes and return of Spongeman.\r\n\r\nLai izdodas!",
      "timestamp_created": 1774131197
    }
